  "title": "Allow refines hooks",
  "body": "Most widgets doing refines should allow to hook into the refine function to allow use cases like:\n- I want to know when the user selected a value\n- I want to go to a specific webpage whent the user click on a menu item\n\nThis would also introduce an API similar to the queryHook on searchBox.\n\nprevious discussion: #791 \n",
